headline: Is Starbucks (SBUX) Pricing Reflecting Recent Mixed Returns And Brand Strength Debates
summary: If you are wondering whether Starbucks at US$86.69 is a bargain or just fairly priced right now, you are not alone. This article aims to unpack what that price tag might really mean for you. Over shorter periods the stock has posted a 2.9% return over 7 days and 3.9% over 30 days. The year to date return of 3.2% sits against a 3.9% decline over 1 year, a 12.3% decline over 3 years, and a 5.7% decline over 5 years.
